<ng-container [ngSwitch]="variant">
    <ng-container *ngSwitchCase="'raised'">
        <button [type]="type" mat-raised-button [color]="color" [disabled]="disabled" (click)="_onClick()">
            <ng-container *ngIf="isLoading">
                <mat-icon class="spinner">
                    <mat-spinner [color]="color" diameter="22">
                    </mat-spinner>
                </mat-icon>
            </ng-container>
            <ng-container *ngIf="!isLoading && icon != '' && iconType == 'fa'">
                <mat-icon [fontSet]="iconType" [fontIcon]="icon"></mat-icon>
            </ng-container>
            <ng-container *ngIf="!isLoading && icon != '' && iconType == 'material'">
                <mat-icon>{{icon}}</mat-icon>
            </ng-container>
            {{name}}
        </button>
    </ng-container>
    <ng-container *ngSwitchCase="'stroked'">
        <button [type]="type" mat-stroked-button [disabled]="disabled" (click)="_onClick()">
            <ng-container *ngIf="isLoading">
                <mat-icon class="spinner">
                    <mat-spinner [color]="color" diameter="22">
                    </mat-spinner>
                </mat-icon>
            </ng-container>
            <ng-container *ngIf="!isLoading && icon != '' && iconType == 'fa'">
                <mat-icon [fontSet]="iconType" [fontIcon]="icon"></mat-icon>
            </ng-container>
            <ng-container *ngIf="!isLoading && icon != '' && iconType == 'material'">
                <mat-icon>{{icon}}</mat-icon>
            </ng-container>
            {{name}}
        </button>
    </ng-container>
    <ng-container *ngSwitchCase="'icon'">
        <button [type]="type" mat-icon-button mat-mini-fab [color]="color" [disabled]="disabled" (click)="_onClick()">
            <ng-container *ngIf="iconType == 'fa'; else materialIcon">
                <mat-icon [fontSet]="iconType" [fontIcon]="icon"></mat-icon>
            </ng-container>
            <ng-template #materialIcon>
                <mat-icon>{{icon}}</mat-icon>
            </ng-template>
        </button>
    </ng-container>
    <ng-container *ngSwitchCase="'icon-non-fab'">
        <button [type]="type" mat-icon-button [color]="color" [disabled]="disabled" (click)="_onClick()">
            <ng-container *ngIf="iconType == 'fa'; else materialIcon">
                <mat-icon [fontSet]="iconType" [fontIcon]="icon"></mat-icon>
            </ng-container>
            <ng-template #materialIcon>
                <mat-icon>{{icon}}</mat-icon>
            </ng-template>
        </button>
    </ng-container>
</ng-container>
